<section id="about" class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
        
        <!-- 1. GİRİŞ BÖLÜMÜ -->
        <h2>Who We Are?</h2>
        <p class="intro-paragraph">
            As Asrın Wallprint, we are a company that always aims for the best in its sector; we are a company that serves with high quality standards, environmentally friendly production and strong design staff. We have always aimed to be the best in this process, which we entered in the 2000s and became a brand in 2015, and we continue on our way by constantly developing in line with this purpose.
        </p>

        <!-- 2. MATERYAL LİSTESİ (İKONLU GRID) -->
        <div class="materials-intro">
            <p>With our Canon and HP printing machines, we carry thousands of original designs on <strong>36 different base materials</strong> and 5 different categories, with a monthly production of 20.000 m2.</p>
        </div>
        
